Products.SmallFormatDescription: Ocean Chef Usa Sea Scallops
Products.FullDescription: Ocean Chef Usa Sea Scallops
Products.RichDescription:
Our juicy scallops are wild caught from the North Atlantic Ocean. Their sweet and tender flesh brings a little bit of luxury to your kitchen.

For maximum flavour caramelise in a hot pan. Pair golden brown scallops with crispy prosciutto and fresh peas for impressive elegance at home.

AdditionalAttributes.description:
Our juicy scallops are wild caught from the North Atlantic Ocean. Their sweet and tender flesh brings a little bit of luxury to your kitchen.

For maximum flavour caramelise in a hot pan. Pair golden brown scallops with crispy prosciutto and fresh peas for impressive elegance at home.
AdditionalAttributes.ingredients:
Sea Scallop, water, salt.
STORAGE:
Store below minus 18°C. Once thawed keep refrigerated below 4°C and consume within 48 hours. Do not refreeze.
THAWING:
To thaw place desired quantitu of scallops in refrigerator at below 4°C for approximately 8 hours. For quicker thawing place scallops in colander and rinse under cold water for 5 - 7 minutes, rotate scallops for even thawing.
